openapi: 3.0.1
info:

servers:

paths:

      operationId: methodWithRequestBodyAndTwoParameters

        200:
          description: default response

          format: int64
        username:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
        password:
          type: string
        phone:
          type: string

          type: integer
          description: User Status
          format: int32
      xml:
        name: User
